31:39.300 --> 31:43.200
talk to each other and tell each other
what we're thinking.

31:43.200 --> 31:45.500
Yes, that would be-- I would--

31:45.500 --> 31:49.400
It would be nice.
We could be confidantes...

31:49.700 --> 31:52.400
confiding confidentially.

31:54.300 --> 31:57.300
[ Whispers ] I've been wanting to do that
for some time now.

31:57.300 --> 31:59.500
[ Both Laugh ]

32:02.000 --> 32:04.100
What do you think of Knox?

32:13.500 --> 32:15.900
What a fantastic entrance.

32:17.500 --> 32:19.400
- Sebassis?
- The nerve.

32:19.400 --> 32:22.000
<i>The raw nerve to lay a hand</i>
<i>on one of mine.!</i>

32:22.000 --> 32:24.400
What is this?
Lower your weapons.

32:24.400 --> 32:27.000
These darts are poisoned,
vampire.

32:27.000 --> 32:29.700
<i>Powerful enough to put you</i>
<i>in a coma for a week.</i>

32:29.700 --> 32:33.200
Enough to kill any one of them
before their next heartbeat.

32:33.200 --> 32:36.500
You murdered Artode.
I imagine we were to be next.

32:36.500 --> 32:39.700
- I didn't murder anyone.
- Dress yourself, Angel.

32:39.700 --> 32:42.000
You have a public execution to attend.

32:43.300 --> 32:46.200
- That's a big mistake.
<i>- [ Woman Screams ]</i>

32:46.200 --> 32:47.800
Move!

32:47.800 --> 32:50.900
- [ Nervous Chattering ]
- Hey!

33:03.800 --> 33:06.500
Oh, boy.

33:06.500 --> 33:09.000
Yeah. Somebody
really dipped his chip.

33:09.000 --> 33:11.200
Okay, Sebassis.
I don't know what's goin' on here...

33:11.200 --> 33:13.700
but we are not behind it.

33:13.700 --> 33:18.000
- Enough lies, vampire.
- Okay, everybody, okay.

33:18.000 --> 33:21.800
Yes, the party's taken
an unfortunate turn momentarily.

33:21.800 --> 33:25.400
- So let's not... fight.
<i>- [ Weapon Clicks ]</i>

33:28.500 --> 33:31.400
''Sleep disorders, Edelmyer complex...

33:31.400 --> 33:33.500
Eldritch causes, empaths.''

33:33.500 --> 33:35.900
Hey, they don't just do sleep here.

33:35.900 --> 33:40.600
Madeline Chu in Accounting,
she had her ennui removed.

33:42.400 --> 33:45.700
Here it is. Lorne's sleep.

33:45.700 --> 33:48.400
Now we just have to find
the delivery device.

33:49.500 --> 33:51.400
This isn't good.

33:51.400 --> 33:53.900
''The effects of
long-term sleeplessness...

33:53.900 --> 33:56.000
on the subconscious mind
of an empath...

33:56.000 --> 33:57.900
can be catastrophic.''

33:57.900 --> 34:00.600
''Catastrophic'' sounds not good.

34:00.600 --> 34:02.600
Under normal conditions...

34:02.600 --> 34:06.200
Lorne has the ability
to read people's destinies...

34:06.200 --> 34:09.400
but now I think
he's writing them.

34:09.400 --> 34:13.100
So what-- instead of receiving,
he's transmitting?

34:13.100 --> 34:15.400
And that's just phase one.

34:15.400 --> 34:19.300
''If you sever the empath
from his subconscious for too long...

34:19.300 --> 34:21.400
that subconscious can--''

34:22.500 --> 34:25.300
It can manifest.

34:25.300 --> 34:27.600
What do you mean, ''manifest''?

34:30.600 --> 34:33.100
<i>Wait. Please wait.</i>
<i>I'm doing this. It's me.</i>

34:33.100 --> 34:36.800
I mean, it's not me.
But I haven't been myself lately.

34:36.800 --> 34:40.000
Somehow, I'm making people do things,
and I'm controlling them.

34:40.000 --> 34:42.199
- [ Chuckles ]
- Whoa!

34:42.199 --> 34:44.600
Well, then, Pylean,
you're making me kill you.

34:44.600 --> 34:46.600
Is that consistent with your theory?

34:46.600 --> 34:48.400
<i>[ Growling ]</i>

34:49.699 --> 34:51.400
<i>- [ Growling Continues ]</i>
- [ Nervous Chatter]

34:51.400 --> 34:53.800
[ Yelling ]

34:56.000 --> 34:58.000
- [ Roaring ]
- Oh, my God!

34:58.000 --> 35:00.400
It's m-me.

35:05.800 --> 35:09.400
That's one bitchin' big suit!

35:09.400 --> 35:11.200
[ Groans ]

35:15.700 --> 35:18.400
- Lorne, what the hell is this?
- Stop it! Stop killing!

35:18.400 --> 35:19.900
<i>Listen to me, me.!</i>

35:22.800 --> 35:25.200
Oh, wow, I must really hate myself.

35:28.400 --> 35:31.400
Oh, come on, come on, come on.

35:34.300 --> 35:36.900
Did-- Did you press--

35:36.900 --> 35:38.800
Oh.

35:40.400 --> 35:42.300
[ Chuckles ]

35:42.300 --> 35:44.100
Yeah.

35:46.400 --> 35:48.800
Come on, come on, come on.

35:49.900 --> 35:51.500
Sebassis, run.

36:04.300 --> 36:07.200
- [ Groaning ]
- Oh, sorry about that.

36:14.900 --> 36:18.600
<i>- [ Blows Landing ]</i>
<i>- [ People Shouting ]</i>

36:18.600 --> 36:20.900
- It's here! It's manifested!
- Angel!

36:27.800 --> 36:30.100
<i>Shoot it, Fred.! Now.!</i>

36:30.100 --> 36:33.200
- Oh. Oh! Oh.
- [ Weapon Fires ]

36:33.200 --> 36:35.500
Oh, my God!
They shot Lorney Tunes!

36:35.500 --> 36:38.100
No, I'm-- I'm okay.

36:39.500 --> 36:42.000
I'm just gonna rest my--
my eyes a little-- a little bit.

36:42.000 --> 36:43.900
[ Growling ]

36:46.700 --> 36:49.100
<i>[ Lorne Snoring ]</i>

37:00.900 --> 37:03.800
[ Snoring Continues ]

37:13.000 --> 37:15.200
<i>- [ Elevator Bell Dings ]</i>
- I gotta hand it to 'em.

37:15.200 --> 37:17.500
- I think this is better than last year.
- [ Both Chuckle ]

37:25.000 --> 37:30.000
Uh, we-- we have people who do that.

37:30.000 --> 37:32.800
Oh.
[ Chuckles ]

37:32.800 --> 37:36.000
- I-- I fixed our baby.
- What?

37:36.000 --> 37:39.400
The-- The stun grenade.
I, uh-- I figured it out.

37:39.400 --> 37:41.400
Oh.

37:41.400 --> 37:44.700
What I can't figure out
is why I said I'd do it tonight.

37:44.700 --> 37:48.300
Yeah. A lot of us are having
that kind of problem.

37:49.800 --> 37:53.500
I kind of wished you were here.

37:54.700 --> 37:56.600
Well, the night is still young.

37:56.600 --> 37:59.500
Well, I mean, no,
it's over, actually.

37:59.500 --> 38:03.900
<i>But, uh, did you-- do you</i>
<i>wanna get a cup of coffee?</i>

38:05.100 --> 38:07.600
Actually, I could use a drink.

38:14.800 --> 38:19.700
That thing-- I think it was
a manifestation of Lorne's subconscious.

38:19.700 --> 38:23.100
It peeled away from his mind,
using Lorne's supernatural powers...

38:23.100 --> 38:25.500
to punch its way into our world.

38:25.500 --> 38:28.000
''Punch'' is the right word.
Why was it trying to kill everyone?

38:28.000 --> 38:30.000
I don't think it was.

38:30.000 --> 38:31.900
It may have just been processing
the conflicts...

38:31.900 --> 38:34.600
that Lorne normally
deals with in his sleep...

38:34.600 --> 38:37.400
acting out on the emotional responses
he has to the people around him.

38:37.400 --> 38:41.700
I guess Lorne makes
some judgments after all. Eve--

38:41.700 --> 38:46.200
So, I guess we should--
I don't know-- talk?

38:46.200 --> 38:48.600
About what?

38:48.600 --> 38:52.400
About what happened,
you know, back there, with us.

38:52.800 --> 38:56.200
Angel, it's not like this is
the first time I've had sex...

38:56.200 --> 38:58.200
under a mystical influence.

38:58.200 --> 39:00.000
I went to U.C. Santa Cruz.

39:02.100 --> 39:03.900
<i>[ Door Opens ]</i>

39:06.500 --> 39:09.300
How you doin'?

39:09.300 --> 39:11.200
I don't know.

39:21.500 --> 39:23.900
- [ Sniffs ]
- [ Laughs ]

39:23.900 --> 39:26.500
I'm a slob.
[ Laughs ]

39:32.300 --> 39:35.300
Hey, I spoke with Sebassis's people,
explained what I could.

39:35.300 --> 39:38.000
Yeah, so what've we got?
Lawsuit? Demon war?

39:38.000 --> 39:41.800
No. Seems like they enjoy a little
blood sport at their social functions.

39:41.800 --> 39:45.500
- Looks like we're okay.
- We're not okay.

39:45.500 --> 39:47.800
We've been so focused
on the dangers outside...

39:47.800 --> 39:50.500
that we didn't see the ones within.

39:50.500 --> 39:54.000
This place is tryin'
to change us, Gunn.

39:54.000 --> 39:55.800
We can't ever forget that.

39:57.400 --> 40:01.100
Pretty damn good party though.
I'll see you tomorrow.

40:01.100 --> 40:03.900
Well, you know, today, but later.

40:03.900 --> 40:06.300
<i>- Oh, and your chair--</i>
- What?

40:06.300 --> 40:09.300
Don't sit in it.
I already called Janitorial.

40:09.300 --> 40:11.600
Why can't I--

40:11.600 --> 40:15.100
You pissed in the big man's chair?
That's fantastic.

40:15.100 --> 40:17.000
Spike, can you please turn off
that warm fuzzy?

40:17.000 --> 40:19.700
What, the Lorne thing? Wore off.
I just think that's bloody fabulous.

40:19.700 --> 40:22.100
All right, guys. Good night.

40:22.100 --> 40:24.600
Let Lorne get some sleep, all right?

40:24.600 --> 40:26.800
Out.

40:26.800 --> 40:29.100
All right.Just this once.

40:32.000 --> 40:34.600
<i>[ Lorne Moans, Mumbles ]</i>

40:34.600 --> 40:36.800
I'm sorry.
[ Mumbling Continues ]

40:36.800 --> 40:39.300
Hey, it's okay, Lorne.

40:39.300 --> 40:42.000
-Just try to get some rest. Get some sleep.
- Mmm.

40:42.000 --> 40:45.800
Yeah. 'Cause it's-- it's hard to--

40:46.100 --> 40:48.600
It's hard bein'--
bein' the host of the party.

40:48.600 --> 40:50.500
Bein'--

40:50.500 --> 40:54.300
Stop tryin' to be.

